{
  "stem": "5496.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And a few days later, we were all taken to Uzhgorod, to Ungvar, where-- it wasn't a ghetto, but it was a gathering area in an old brick factory, which was, like, in the open.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's where, obviously, they brought in everyone from the neighboring villages and towns.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's where we stayed-- and mercifully, I don't remember how long-- under very primitive condition, until we were taken, then, by train on that fateful day to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "How long we stayed there, I have no recollection.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, none.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a child, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I only remember-- vaguely, I remember that my father told my mother to hide her engaged-- her-- obviously, her wedding band and her engagement ring.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But no personal possession that I recall at all, that I had taken along.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, this was after school that we found out, and we never returned to school again.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was abrupt, sudden, and without, so to speak, really any prior warning.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was where the Hungarians had taken us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I will never forgive them, because they were worse than the Germans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They did it on their own, over-zealously.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they herded us all in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My grandmother, who-- I forgot to say.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In the meantime, my grandfather passed away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my grandmother lived with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So it was my grandmother, my Aunt Rose, my mother and father, and my sister.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were all in this little cubicle, which wasn't much privacy, because the whole thing was an open area.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Still, we stuck together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the only thing I remember is that one day, my grandmother complained-- may she rest in peace-- that she was hungry.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we couldn't give her anything, because there was none.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Aunt Rose's son fled.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
